### 1. GET - Retrieve all tasks
GET http://localhost:3000/api/todos
Accept: application/json

###

### 2. POST - Create a new task
POST http://localhost:3000/api/todos
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Learn TypeScript"
}

###

### 3. PUT - Update an existing task (with ID 1)
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/todos/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Learn TypeScript with TypeORM",
  "completed": true
}

###

### 4. DELETE - Delete an existing task (with ID 1)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/todos/1
